title: The Patriots No Longer Look Like the Patriots | The Ringer NFL Show (Ep. 366)
description:
The Patriots might not have enough to make the Super Bowl this year, Nick Foles the king is back, and the Rams offense is in a spiral (0:30). Plus, the Colts' late-season push, the Cowboys' goose egg, Seattle’s bizarre loss to San Francisco, and tomorrow’s headlines (20:30).
Hosts: Robert Mays and Kevin Clark
